reviews.text: Not a real vietnam restaurant,  and the vietnam coffee is so Hong Kong flavour.

I am very disappointed with the change in the operation mode in this restaurant. I've been a customer for several years. I loved the food and service provided before. Now many things are different.
1. menu: lack of Vietnamese style. Most of the food is like Hong Kong style noodles (車仔麵)
2. eating utensils: give out disposable ones (including chopsticks, spoon, cup and bowl). When other restaurants are encouraging customers not to use disposable utensils. This restaurant is doing the reverse way. The manager is not having any sense of social responsibility and environmental conservation.
3. service: (i) Previously, the waitress would take order for the customers. Now, customers are asked to mark their order on a cardboard with white board marker. (ii) In addition, when some customers requested for a glass of water, the manager asked them to get at the counter themselves. Even though no service charge is included in the bill, getting a glass of water for the customers is so simple. Asking customers to walk around would only cost chaos in the restaurant. (iii) The manager and waitress were careless and knocked over the drinks which spill over on the floor.

Obviously the change in the operation mode is to cut cost and maximize profit. Yet I definitely would not visit this restaurant ever again. The manager indeed saved some cost, but also the profit will be less unfortunately.

叫漢堡飯, 佢煎到兩面全燶俾我, 我俾番佢, 不過阿姐處理得幾好, 同埋幾好聲氣, 算. 試過凍奶茶, 完全無甜味, 叫佢加番俾我, 算.試過咖喱牛腩飯, 有成八舊薯仔, 但得二舊牛腩, 叫阿姐follow, 跟住廚房加番幾舊牛腩俾我, 算. 試過早咗入去, 問佢有無午餐, 佢話都有, 我落咗單等咗30分鐘, 人地遲入嚟果d 午餐嚟哂仲食梗我個都未嚟, 叫佢check, 30秒即出到俾我, 算. 我仲有去食, 因為間野冷氣夠涼, 同埋氣氛啱我, 除咗某d 時間會有d 嘈人搞串party 外, 其他時間幾靜, 同埋wifi 夠快, 不過似乎有登入數限制, 人多會login 唔到.
味道好、有特色;尤其是沙冰真材實料,超水準！
我沒有來過這裡，所以不知道
